Highlights

  • Be enchanted by the beauty of the sunset as the sky fills with different shades of orange and pink.
  • Sail in a yacht that is the epitome of luxury and romance, making it perfect for the couples.
  • Dive in the unbridled beauty of the Arabian sea as you set sail from Porvorim.
  • Cruise through the turquoise waters and enjoy the undiscovered views of Mandovi river during sunset or sunrise.

Overview

Cater to your love for the sea, embark on a voyage to a one-of-a-kind vacation that will surely help you create some of the most amazing memories that you will cherish for a lifetime. You can sunbathe on the deck, while the cold breeze passes through your hair. The yacht is tailor-made to provide you with the most luxurious experience possible.

About the activity-

  • The cruise provides a breathtaking view of Goa from the Arabian sea.
  • Avail of additional services such as catering, event decorations, drone photography, and videography.
  • Depending on your preference you can either decide to take a 1-hour cruise or a 2-hour one.
  • Trace down the enthralling beauty that lies on the shores of Goa with the beautiful seascape.
  • The cruise's operational time is from 6:00 AM to 7:00 PM, and it can accommodate up to 10 people.
  • The boarding point is Britona(Porvorim) and is easily reachable via public or private transport. This place is located at a distance of 7km from Panjim.
